parameters: Hello, big sister! This is Bukkoro Village!!

It's quite a dangerous-sounding name for a village... Why is
it called that?

Grandpa said it's because they raise livestock and sell them
as meat!
Oh... We must be grateful for life.
What would happen if I attacked this thing...?
Oh no, a little boy is crying!

What's wrong? If something happened, please tell us sisters
about it.

*sob*... *sniffle*...!! I got separated from Pochi... lost
in the forest...

Please don't cry. We sisters will find your Pochi and bring
him back to you.
Yes! Leave it to us sisters. Let's go, Memerisu-chan!
I'm not really fond of animals though...

We got separated from Pochi in the forest to the southeast.
Big sisters, please find Pochi...

Yes, I've brought back the lost Pochi-kun. Please don't cry
anymore

Thank you, big sisters! As a token of my gratitude, I'll
give you this pretty stone I found in the forest!
Thank you very much. I'll take good care of it.
No problem, if you have any other troubles, please tell me.

No problem, if you have any other troubles, just let me
know.
Big sis, really? Actually, I'm having another problem...
Oh? What seems to be the trouble this time?

It turns out we're not allowed to keep Pochi in the
village...
Ah, so Pochi wasn't a pet dog after all...
What should I do, big sis...
This is troubling... What should we do...

Why not take care of Pochi in Chern village? You can also go
check on him from time to time.

That's a great idea! You do come up with good suggestions
sometimes

So, how about it? How about we take care of Pochi in our
village?

Yeah, sure! Big sis, please take good care of Pochi! I'll
come to play too!
Shota and Pochi have joined your party!
It's a well! Let's drink some water!
I need to pee, so maybe I should hold off for now...
Memerisu drew water and drank it!
Memerisu's health has been fully restored!

...Hmm, I kind of feel like I need to go to the bathroom
now.

Memerisu now needs to pee! She has to go to the bathroom or
she'll wet herself!

I also feel like peeing right now... Let's not drink any
more.
Tina drew water and drank it!
It's cold and tasty... It's refreshing
Tina's health has been fully restored!

Ah... I kind of feel like I need to go to the bathroom a
little now.

Tina now needs to pee! She has to go to the bathroom or
she'll wet herself!
It will be 10G per night. Will you be staying?

Ladies... if you have sweet potatoes, roasting them over a
campfire makes them sweet and delicious.

I love roasted sweet potatoes! Let's go buy some sweet
potatoes somewhere!
I'm pretty sure the nearby shop sells them

Wow, there's a campfire! I happen to have some sweet
potatoes, maybe I'll make some baked sweet potatoes~

Yes, they're nicely baked~ Be careful not to burn yourself,
it's hot.

Yay~! They look fluffy and delicious! Tina-chan, let's eat
them together later

Oh, there's a campfire. If I had some sweet potatoes, I'd
want to make baked sweet potatoes.
